text: Jennifer Pettke (born 29 May 1989) is a German national volleyball player. She played at the 2014 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2014 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2016 European Olympic Qualification Tournament, 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. She played for Rote Raben Vilsbiburg. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:German volleyball players
